/span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">Period</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(start, end);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk12\">end</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">setYear</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk7\">2010</span><span class=\"mtk1\">); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// p 내부를 수정함으로써 start가 end보다 작다는 불변식이 깨졌습니다!</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>이런 외부 공격으로부터 인스턴스 내부를 보호하려면 매개변수를 방어적으로 복사해야 합니다.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"java\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">public</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">Period</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk10\">Date</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> start, </span><span class=\"mtk10\">Date</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> end) {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">this</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk12\">start</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk15\">new</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">Date</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">start</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">getTime</span><span class=\"mtk1\">()); </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 방어적 복사</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">this</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk12\">end</span><span class=\"mtk1\">   = </span><span class=\"mtk15\">new</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">Date</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">end</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.</span><span class=\"mtk11\">getTime</span><span class=\"mtk1\">());   </span><span class=\"mtk3\">// 방어적 복사</spa